Definition: Given an input word generate a word that rhymes exactly with the input word. If not rhyme is found return "No"

Positive Examples.explanation: The word difficult has no natural English rhymes and so the model outputs No as specified in the instructions.
The output is a word that rhymes exactly with the input word.

Negative Examples.explanation: Here the model outputs an example of a planet in response to the prompt word instead of following the directions and generating a rhyming word.
The model generates a blank string when it cannot find any rhymes instead of returning "No" as specified in the instructions
